{
  "stem": "33.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because we had to pay the Jews for the maintenance of the-- of those little cottages-- and we didn't.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I guess the second year, we kids did go back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I suppose they did apologize or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The-- our parents never went back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They decided that they are not going to go where they're not wanted.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But we had nothing else to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Traveling was impossible, because we couldn't cross borders anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Jews we're not allowed-- Jews didn't have passports in the '40s.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So the only traveling we could do was in the country or visiting family going to Budapest, maybe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And us kids needed something for the summer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we did go back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But little things like this happened that made life, temporarily, at least, miserable.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But basically, our life was normal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This all came to an end in March of 1944 where-- when the German Army physically occupied Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Up until that time, and especially starting in 1943, we started to be very optimistic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because as soon as the siege of Leningrad and Stalingrad was over, and tides turned around, we knew that they're going to lose the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And every day that we still stayed in our homes, every day-- well, I'm not talking about us youngsters-- but our parents and their peers were more and more optimistic.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because there it was, 1942, 1943, 1944 started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They were losing on all fronts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were still in our homes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I guess it's also human nature, because for some reason, whatever happened to my neighbor is not going to happen to me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Because for some reason, we always think that we are different from our neighbors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And that was basically true.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I think the dividing line was very apparent on-- between your assimilated and your religious Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
